Hindi man kami magkamag-anak ni Huang Liang.

149
00:08:19,300 --> 00:08:20,460
Bakit ko itatanggi ang sarili ko?

150
00:08:21,500 --> 00:08:22,340
Tingnan mo,

151
00:08:22,900 --> 00:08:24,250
