176
00:09:13,420 --> 00:09:14,720
Hindi ko nakitang magalang ka noon.

177
00:09:15,620 --> 00:09:17,300
Si Huang Liang ay isang malaking boss ngayon.

178
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,860
Hongbing, tingnan mo ang sinasabi mo.

179
00:09:18,860 --> 00:09:19,740
