pinagmamasdan ito ng 30 taon?

208
00:10:04,180 --> 00:10:05,020
Hindi.

209
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,060
Hongbing, mangyaring huwag.

210
00:10:06,060 --> 00:10:07,380
Hindi mo ito magagawa. Hindi.

211
00:10:07,380 --> 00:10:08,240
Huwag gawin ito.

212
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,300
Hongbing, huwag mong buksan.

213
00:10:09,300 --> 00:10:11,180
I-save ang alak na ito para sa araw ng kasal ni Hui.

214
00:10:11,180 --> 00:10:12,370
Tapos bubuksan natin, okay?

215
00:10:14,260 --> 00:10:15,100
Binuksan mo talaga.

216
00:10:15,100 --> 00:10:15,940
Sa aming linya ng trabaho,

217
00:10:16,980 --> 00:10:18,180
