para sa malaking araw ng batang lalaki?

220
00:10:21,620 --> 00:10:22,460
Halika na.

221
00:10:23,860 --> 00:10:24,820
Salamat, Hongbing.

222
00:10:24,820 --> 00:10:25,660
Huang Liang.

223
00:10:26,900 --> 00:10:28,420
Ang dahilan kung bakit kita pinatawag dito ngayon

224
00:10:29,180 --> 00:10:30,580
